Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:15.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.73,0:00:23.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:27.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:34.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:45.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:53.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:56.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:04.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:08.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:11.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:15.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:19.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.02,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(477.167,230.389)}The {\fnOne Stroke Script LET}8 {\fnCienfuegos}Kamen Riders
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:35.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The terrifying Gel Shocker\Nhas created the Shocker Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,identical in appearance\Nto the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:40.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Shocker Rider's goal is to frame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:44.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the ally of justice, Kamen\NRider, for his own evil deeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:47.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and to destroy the Anti-Shocker Alliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:51.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,which possesses a tape containing\Nthe secret of Shocker's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:56.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In addition, the Kamen Rider\Nhas been plunged into terrible peril
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,at the hands of the Shocker\NRider and Flytrap Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I will truly take your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me be the one to finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is gone,\Nalong with Flytrap Bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I am the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no further need for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw it away just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not, Raydokuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Change of orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be taking a fake Gel Shocker\Ntape to the Anti-Shocker Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's to be run\Nthrough Gel Shocker's computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's in that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A tape recording of killer sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer sound waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Anti-Shocker Alliance will\Nfoolishly put this in their computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then, they'll all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give them an act. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. This is all we need!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished off the fake Rider\Nand the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Fake Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Gel Shocker...\NThey even created a fake Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that to the Anti-Shocker\NAlliance at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call, Shocker Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They almost found you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But that should keep them\Nin the dark a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That fake tape will soon put an end
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to all members of that\Nimpudent organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the Anti-Shocker Alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will complete a litany\Nof evils in Kamen Rider's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Anti-Shocker Alliance's tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it into the computer, General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing how much\Nthey've learned about me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,will give us an idea of the scale\Nof the Anti-Shocker Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be an interesting test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put it into the computer at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:43.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We gave the tape to a certain someone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in order to outwit Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On January 6th, at noon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:55.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that person will arrive in\NAnti-Shocker's computer room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only one hour until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Call off the plan to destroy\Nthe Anti-Shocker Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We must steal the real\Ntape from them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This will give us the identity\Nof Gel Shocker's leader, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that we'll soon achieve\Nwhat we've dreamed of for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost feel frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning it on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This tape is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning it on would make it explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me, I'll test it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably leave this\Nin Rider's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Cover your ears and get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd turned it on,\Nyou would have all been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, where in the world\Nis the real computer tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The real one is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,South America's Anti-Shocker\NAlliance chose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to spend New Year's\Nat home, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kogure, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... when did your scarf change?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad it's too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji, congratulations\Non completing your long errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But this case belongs\Nto the Shocker Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let some Shocker Rider have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Go after the Shocker Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape me, Shocker Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake is a fake from start to finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill me,\Nyour allies will die as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The second Shocker Rider has already\Ninfiltrated the Rider Kid Corps headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a second Shocker Rider, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Headquarters is in danger! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki!\N- The Rider Corps headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:25.09,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my New Year's gift to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A New Year's gift from Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting a New Year's gift\Nfrom Kamen Rider is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see what's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... what is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker monster Raydokuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a New Year's gift at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like my gift, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose not... since it's\Na gift from the Shocker Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've realized it too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,None of you will escape alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a break for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathing in my poison powder will\Nput you to sleep for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be hostages. Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's computer predicted\Na 90% chance that you were alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we needed hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But your plan to get hostages has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... you can sleep, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki! Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not your usual lively self...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course... were you injured\Nwhen you fell with Flytrap Bee?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... you can't beat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi! Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hongo!\N- Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They took the others hostage,\Nright under my nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! Stay with us, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be from a member of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Headquarters here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.07,Italics,,0,0,0,,Would this be Captain Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice... General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:59.01,Italics,,0,0,0,,I have five hostages from your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Return the women and children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a coward's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll happily return the hostages\Nif you give us what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:15.38,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'll trade them for the computer tape\Nin the Anti-Shocker Alliance's possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.51,Italics,,0,0,0,,The location is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana, I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This tape represents the rage\Nthat thousands feel for Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But... the lives of our allies in the fight\Nagainst Gel Shocker are also on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you... please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but our members voted,\Nand this was the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who\Nasked us for help in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll retrieve the hostages ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-Shocker Alliance, my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe how\Nself-centered they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please avenge my mother\Nwho was killed by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't this make trouble for you later?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going to the meeting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, you're in no condition for this yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They have two Shocker\NRiders on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I can just\Nsit back, doing nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still can't let you come...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think you can stop Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place they said to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where they're hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought the tape, as promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the hostages?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:50.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We need to make sure\Nthe tape is real first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us the hostages first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As you will see, they're safe and sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Takeshi!\N- Mr. Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now, we'll confirm the tape's authenticity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Captain Taki. Walk forward, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Riders...\Ndestroy the three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Riders?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Rider No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Rider No. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Rider No. 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Rider No. 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Rider No. 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Rider No. 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show them what true strength is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:55.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Shocker Riders have\Nshown their full hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:58.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,before the first and\Nsecond Kamen Riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:22:59.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are six of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:04.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can the double Riders\Nbeat the Shocker Riders?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:06.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight, Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.05,Cont,,0,80,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.68,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:14.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The battle to retrieve\Nthe mystery tape continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:17.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taki remains clinging\Nto the ascending helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:22.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The six Shocker Riders use stunning\Ncooperative tactics to attack our Riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:24.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:27.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The True Identity of\NGel Shocker's Leader!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:31.20,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx120\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,160.389)}The True Identity of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:31.20,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)}Gel Shocker's Leader!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:39.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:42.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:46.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:49.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:54.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.21,0:24:01.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:06.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:12.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\fnOne Stroke Script LET}8 {\fnCienfuegos}Kamen Riders
Comment: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The True Identity of\NGel Shocker's Leader!!